title: Garmin MapSource Italy Topo Garda & Dolomit v2
description:
TrekMap Lago di Garda e Dolomiti 
MapSource version in .iso format
 

GPS of Garmin are transformed in true "Navigators from Montagna" thanks
to the topographical cartography TrekMap.

Garmin and Lieta to announce the launch of the first portion of
topographical cartography of the Italian territory: the area currently
available covers two locality of detail tourist and sport interest: the
north of the Lake of Garda and its mountains, and a good portion of the
Dolomites.

Manufacturer's homepage: <a href="
